item.description: Come to the Food Project's Farm in Lincoln, MA (a beautiful 30 minute walk from the Lincoln commuter rail stop - very close to Walden Pond!) for our first ever seedling sale! It helps to support the Food Project's mission (thefoodproject.org) and we'll have over 60 different varieties of flowers, herbs, and vegetables! Saturday, Sunday, and Monday 10am-3pm.
item.name: The Food Project Seedling Sale
